txt.en: The Wargs of Ujâk-fulug will soon cross the hills and valleys beyond their den, and when they do the folk who live and adventure in the Floodfells will be in danger. They must be defeated before this can happen.
You defeated many wargs in Ujâk-fulug, ensuring the safety of the folk who live in the Floodfells.
Wargs have made a den in Ujâk-fulug, and they must be defeated before they can threaten the people of the Floodfells.
Wargs have made a den in Ujâk-fulug, and they must be defeated before they can threaten the people of the Floodfells.
A dangerous warg-pack has made its home within Ujâk-fulug, and should be defeated before it crosses the hills to menace the folk who live within the Floodfells.
TBD Floodfells has become a haven of the foul Wargs.\n\nYou should defeat wargs in Floodfells and Ujâk-fulug.
Your efforts against the Wargs of Ujâk-fulug have made safer the lives of those who live in the Floodfells.
